data.description: Price is negotiable! Stunning 4 bed/ 2 bath single family home w pool in Cypress Glen w over 2,400 sqft of living area. Home shows like a model and features porcelain floors throughout, large living room w vaulted ceilings & fireplace. Remodeled kitchen w stainless steel appliances, kitchen opens to the family room w views of the pool & screened patio area great for entertainment. Spacious master w/door to the pool & direct access to 4th room/office/nursery. Home fully completed w impact windows & doors including french doors & impact skylights. Roof 2003, AC 2021, Water Heater 2020. New flat roof 2021.The house includes security system 4 cameras and ring doorbell. Great location short walk/drive to shopping, schools, hospitals, entertainment, & highways. No HOA. Sale doesn't include W/D
